text.tspan: Okay, thanks for letting me know! One question I do have is
about this group, is this the main group for the design team or
is there a separate chat? I’m just trying to understand.
Since you were already working within the company for another
position, it won’t long until you have access to all of our files.
We are all excited to have you, we loved the work that you
showed us during your interview and you fit well with everyone
on our team and company. If you have any questions feel free
to ask and someone on the team will help you out.
Thank you, I’m so excited to join this amazing design team! I’m
very grateful to have the opportunity to work on some products
that will impact people's lives. I can’t wait to get started!
Hi Justin! We just wanted to welcome you to our team.
